* The Eobard Thawne version of Reverse-Flash appears a playable character in
* The Eobard Thawne version of Reverse-Flash appears as a DLC skin in Injustice 2.
* The Eobard Thawne version of Reverse-Flash appears as a playable character in Lego DC Super-Villains, and The Flash's version of Zoom appears in the DC TV Super-Villains DLC pack.
